p speed of nearly 825 miles per hour.""CNN reports that the jet landed nearly two hours ahead of schedule at Heathrow airport at 4:43 am.""The plane was faster by one minute than a Virgin Airways A350 that also took advantage of the jet stream."SOURCES: Flightradar24.com, CNN https://www.flightradar24.com/blog/british-airways-sets-new-transatlantic-speed-record/https://edition.cnn.com/travel/article/british-airways-fast-flight-scli-intl-gbr/index.html***]]></description>
