eceipt once they have exited the store."SOURCES: New Atlas, 7-11, Tech Crunch, 21 CBS DFWhttps://newatlas.com/good-thinking/7-eleven-trial-no-cashiers/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/7-eleven-pilots-cashierless-store-concept-300999252.htmlhttps://techcrunch.com/2020/02/06/7-eleven-is-the-next-retailer-to-test-cashierless-stores/https://dfw.cbslocal.com/2020/02/05/7-eleven-tests-cashierless-store-texas/***]]></description>
